signatures.text: fun <K : Comparable<K>, V> Map<out K, V>.toSortedMap(): SortedMap<K, V>
signatures.desc: Converts this Map to a SortedMap. The resulting SortedMap determines the equality and order of keys according to their natural sorting order.

signatures.text: fun <K, V> Map<out K, V>.toSortedMap( comparator: Comparator<in K>): SortedMap<K, V>
signatures.desc: Converts this Map to a SortedMap. The resulting SortedMap determines the equality and order of keys according to the sorting order provided by the given comparator.
